     C           *IN97     IFEQ *ON
     C                     WRITEAB#EP701
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
      *          INITIALIZE
